# This is a SECRET key for the Firebase Admin SDK (used for server-side operations).
# Generate this from your Firebase project settings: Project settings > Service accounts > Generate new private key.
# Then, you MUST encode the entire JSON file to Base64.
# - On macOS/Linux: base64 -w 0 path/to/your/serviceAccountKey.json
# - On Windows (PowerShell): [Convert]::ToBase64String([IO.File]::ReadAllBytes("path/to/your/serviceAccountKey.json"))
FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY_BASE64="...PASTE_YOUR_BASE64_ENCODED_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY_HERE..."


